content:
Wakha 😄 hada code JavaScript sakhl bach ijiblek random number:

```javascript
// random number bin 0 w 1 (float)
const r1 = Math.random();
console.log(r1);

// random integer bin 1 w 10
const r2 = Math.floor(Math.random() * 10) + 1;
console.log(r2);
```

`Math.random()` kat3tik nombre bin 0 w 1, w `Math.floor` kat7ydo les décimales. Ila bghiti range safi qol liya.
